<HEADLINE>
CALLING ALL SWAT TEAMS: THE LATEST BUZZ FROM CALIFORNIA 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
