</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-APPALACHIA-REVIEW-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
APPALACHIA: FOR BETTER AND WORSE, POVERTY'S POSTER CHILD 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (ART ADV: Graphic is being sent to NYT graphic clients.
