prevalent in America.
</P>
<P>
   ``Androstenedione is a steroid,'' he added. ``There's no
question about it. It shouldn't be available.''
</P>
<P>
   Dr. Charles Yesalis, co-author of ``The Steroids Game,'' is
frequently asked how androstenedione can be sold legally over the
counter.
</P>
<P>
   ``I say: `It beats me. It makes no sense at all,''' Yesalis
said.
</P>
