<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
July 11 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Brad Nelson at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
SOC-WORLD (Pasadena) _ U.S. wins Women's World Cup. 
By Fred J. Robledo/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
SOC-CROUSE-COLUMN (Pasadena) _ Column from soccer game. 
